channel.title: Help? Loading char profiles please log in again?
channel.description: Well, I was trying to start up a server, and I was planning on running it on Hamachi with a few friends who were helping me with the server, to see what we should add/change/get rid of. Although, whenever we try logging in using my client, it says "Loading char profile, please log in again, and even with the moparscape client, it said the same! If anybody can help me, please e-mail me at spazzytazzy268@hotmail.com (I made it when I was 6, don't judge.) Thanks, and please include if I can ask you for help if needed.
